  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is two-fold. First we would like to confirm that non-contact ECG
      provides equivalency to current contact methods of obtaining ECG data. Second we would like
      to investigate whether non-contact ECG can detect ECG changes prior to the onset symptoms
      from COVID19.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
